| ID                               | Name     |
+----------------------------------+----------+
| e66d97ac1b704897853412fc8450f7b9 | admin    |
| bf4a37b885fe46bd86e999e50adad1d3 | services |
| 21bd1c7c95234fd28f589b60903606fa | tenant01 |
| f599c5cd1cba4125ae3d7caed08e288c | tenant02 |
+----------------------------------+----------+</literal_block>
            <paragraph>To display all current users for a project, run:</paragraph>
            <literal_block highlight_args="{}" language="console" linenos="False" xml:space="preserve">$ openstack user list --project PROJECT_NAME
+----------------------------------+--------+
| ID                               | Name   |
+----------------------------------+--------+
| ea30aa434ab24a139b0e85125ec8a217 | demo00 |
| 4f8113c1d838467cad0c2f337b3dfded | demo01 |
+----------------------------------+--------+</literal_block>
        </note>
        <paragraph>Use <literal classes="samp" role="samp">openstack quota show <emphasis>PROJECT_NAME</emphasis></literal> to list all quotas for a
            project.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>Use <literal classes="samp" role="samp">openstack quota set <emphasis>PROJECT_NAME</emphasis> <emphasis>--parameters</emphasis></literal> to set quota
            values.</paragraph>
